name: Identity Crisis (THE GREAT OVERLORD OF ALL CHEESE)
name_original: Identity Crisis (THE GREAT OVERLORD OF ALL CHEESE)
description:
This is a short first-person shooter focused on fighting AI enemies to reach the end of the level. It features 2 levels, 3 main enemy types and is fairly difficult, so try your best! At the end of the game, there is a stats screen so you can check your completion time!

Controls:
WASD & Mouse - Movement
Space - Jump
Shift - Run
Left Mouse - Fire
R - Reload
developers: THE GREAT OVERLORD OF ALL CHEESE
